rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Hiyokkoo hearing more and more
reports of monsters attacking salvagers
in Cloud Sea lately.

rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It harder to move down there, so if
monsters attack, escape not much
of an option.

rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Lots of salvagers too afraid to dive
now. Frozen with scary-scares.

rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
It put Hiyokkoo off too, so Hiyokkoo is
just enjoying view from here.

rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Maybe if Hiyokkoo had bodyguard,
would have courage to dive...

rows.label: tlk42410111_05_msg0008
rows.name:
Ooh-hoo-hoo! Much relief!
Hiyokkoo so happy to hear!
